         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>(To) . . . (from) Psenamounios, bishop . . . greetings in the Lord God. I rejoice exceedingly having found the opportunity that I have been granted to send a letter to your Excellency together with all, great and small, of your blessed house. I do not cease to remember day and night the longing for the love which you have shown to . . . May God and his Christ preserve you and . . .

</ab>
